sg"></p><ul class="list-paddingleft-1" style="list-style-type: disc;"><li><p style="min-height: 24px;margin: 16px 8px 24px;"><span style="color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgb(48, 48, 48);">首先是界面简洁清晰、操作简单，老少皆宜，有手就会！AI软件国产之光嘛！</span></p></li><li><p style="min-height: 24px;margin: 16px 8px 24px;"><span style="color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgb(48, 48, 48);">其次是很用心产品运营上，比如一目了然的提示语“文件拖进来，网址发出来”，滚动式把核心功能介绍清楚，同时满足了年轻用户群体的需求。</span></p></li></ul><div style="margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;font-size: 16px;"><div powered-by="xiumi.us" style="will-change: transform;"><div style="margin-top: 48px;margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: left;"><div style="padding-left: 30px;display: inline-block;min-width: 10%;vertical-align: top;"><div powered-by="xiumi.us" style="margin-bottom: -30px;transform: translate3d(-30px, 0px, 0px);"><div style="display: inline-block;width: 30px;height: 30px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;border-width: 0px;border-radius: 100%;border-style: none;border-color: rgba(118, 178, 124, 0);background-color: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);"><div powered-by="xiumi.us" style="text-align: justify;"><p><br></p></div></div></div><div powered-by="xiumi.us" style="transform: translate3d(-15px, 0px, 0px);"><div style="padding-top: 3px;padding-bottom: 3px;display: inline-block;min-width: 10%;vertical-align: top;"><div powered-by="xiumi.us" style="font-size: 20px;color: rgb(55, 80, 114);text-align: justify;"><p><strong>一些好玩儿的</strong></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><p style="min-height: 24px;margin: 16px 8px 24px;"><span style="color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgb(48, 48, 48);">有不少开发者通过API接口捏出了很多好玩、好用和有创造力的应用，感兴趣的可以试试看：</span></p><ul class="list-paddingleft-1" style="list-style-type: disc;"><li><p style="min-h